in the future,

35:53.067 --> 35:54.967
and I feel like I learned
a lot, you know?

35:55.067 --> 35:56.667
It's hard not to learn
a lot, I mean,

35:56.733 --> 35:59.000
your eyes are closed
if you're not learning.

36:01.333 --> 36:02.600
Not getting a moose
just means like,

36:02.667 --> 36:04.100
I'm gonna have to snare
a lot of rabbits,

36:04.167 --> 36:05.700
shoot a lot of grouse,

36:05.933 --> 36:07.067
